Baggers Magazine - June 2014  USA

124 Pages | True PDF | English | 26 MB 


What do you get when you cross a screaming V-twin bike, add the comforts of a luxury sedan for better touring, and toss it in a magazine? You get BAGGERS, a magazine packed with motorcycle information!  Baggers was created for folks who enjoy not just the bike, but the journey too. Our editors promise to give you everything you need to get you going before your next road trip.
